Rust-native CI runner

Usage: ci <COMMAND>

Commands:
  budget   Placeholder for the budget pipeline
  publish  Placeholder for the publish pipeline
  doctor   Print tool versions and environment diagnostics
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

